1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 19=
(Acting)

3
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:25,480
Promise me.

4
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,400
What?

5
00:01:28,719 --> 00:01:29,560
After the sun rises,

6
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,319
don't leave me.

7
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:34,040
I want to wake up
in the arms of the one I love.

8
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:40,540
♪To explain this ambiguous
flutter of the heart♪

9
00:01:40,980 --> 00:01:44,140
♪The wind suddenly
turns romantic and light♪

10
00:01:44,460 --> 00:01:47,700
♪Leaving me unsure♪

11
00:01:49,820 --> 00:01:53,820
♪How to put this feeling into words♪

12
00:01:54,460 --> 00:01:59,060
♪I find myself longing for a response♪

13
00:01:59,060 --> 00:02:02,540
♪Missing you, tangled and unresolved♪

14
00:02:02,540 --> 00:02:07,660
♪I need your reply♪

15
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:10,140
♪Why when I'm close to you♪

16
00:02:10,140 --> 00:02:12,260
♪My heart grows restless♪

17
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:14,580
♪Why is it only you♪

18
00:02:14,580 --> 00:02:17,100
♪Who clears the sky of my world♪

19
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:21,180
♪Has love quietly arrived♪

20
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:26,140
♪You and I are meant to be♪

21
00:02:26,140 --> 00:02:28,420
♪Why did you barge into♪

22
00:02:28,420 --> 00:02:30,780
♪My lonely story♪

23
00:02:30,780 --> 00:02:32,900
♪Why do my eyes♪

24
00:02:32,900 --> 00:02:35,300
♪Keep chasing you♪

25
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:40,380
♪Even if the sky falls to the ground♪

26
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:47,479
This ruthless woman.

27
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,319
One night, and she's gone again.

28
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,520
Here.

29
00:02:58,639 --> 00:02:59,039
Dad.

30
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:02,719
The resort's reputation
has just turned around,

31
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:05,000
I think pushing for an acquisition now

32
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:05,960
would not be wise.

33
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,479
We should slow down

34
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,560
and wait for a safer bet.

35
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:14,639
Then when would be the right time?

36
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:19,800
Jinxi and Shaoze's engagement banquet
is coming up.

37
00:03:20,159 --> 00:03:21,560
I plan to take that opportunity

38
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:23,240
to completely win Gu Qingmei over

39
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:25,400
and make her devoted to me.

40
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,080
Then the entire Gu Corporation

41
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,400
will fall into my hands.

42
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,120
And the resort

43
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,319
will naturally be mine.

44
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:35,360
That might just work.

45
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:38,400
But don't forget

46
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:42,319
your real goal.

47
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,120
Don't worry.

48
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:47,240
I know exactly what I am doing.

49
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,560
You may go.

50
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,560
Did you hear all that?

51
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,800
While you were away,

52
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,919
your dear sister

53
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:11,120
not only took your place

54
00:04:12,319 --> 00:04:14,240
but also took your husband.

55
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:18,040
Your husband is completely
obsessed with her.

56
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:20,120
Qingmei,

57
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,160
it's time for you to come back

58
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,959
and take back everything

59
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,360
that is rightfully yours.

60
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:31,839
I will.

61
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,560
Congratulations.

62
00:04:44,639 --> 00:04:46,399
You successfully resolved
the resort crisis

63
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:49,240
and reclaimed your position
as Chairman of Gu Corporation.

64
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,000
As long as you stop using

65
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,480
dirty tricks,

66
00:04:54,759 --> 00:04:55,720
I will be grateful.

67
00:04:57,439 --> 00:04:58,040
I know

68
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,959
you have a lot of resentment toward me

69
00:05:02,079 --> 00:05:03,360
over the resort acquisition.

70
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,120
But you have misunderstood me.

71
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:07,240
Manager Lin did all of it
behind my back.

72
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:08,639
I only just found out.

73
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:10,480
I have already fired him.

74
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,240
Is that so?

75
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,040
You have to trust me.

76
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:15,680
For you,

77
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,279
I have already suspended
all acquisition plans.

78
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:18,480
I will use every resource

79
00:05:19,199 --> 00:05:20,360
to help you revive the resort.

80
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,519
He Jinchen,

81
00:05:21,839 --> 00:05:23,160
I can give you a break,

82
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,560
but only if you use your brain.

83
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:27,439
Do you really think
I would believe that?

84
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,199
No...

85
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:42,920
From now on,

86
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:45,319
I'm pulling out of the acquisition.

87
00:05:46,439 --> 00:05:47,560
What do you want?

88
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,439
Dear,

89
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:51,639
I love you.

90
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:53,560
I never

91
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,399
appreciated you before.

92
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:56,639
From now on,

93
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:58,720
I will make it up to you.

94
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,879
Hold on... Dear?

95
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:02,160
How did you bring yourself to say that?

96
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:04,680
You know I'm not the real Gu Qingmei.

97
00:06:06,839 --> 00:06:08,879
Even if you regain your memory,
it doesn't matter.

98
00:06:09,399 --> 00:06:11,439
I've decided, that's it.

99
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,480
Then what if

100
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:19,120
the real Gu Qingmei comes back?

101
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:20,519
How would you make your selection?

102
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:24,319
You, of course.

103
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:25,720
In my heart,

104
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,560
you are my wife.

105
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,879
If you want to keep up this act,

106
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,639
I will play along.

107
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:45,720
(Charity Recovery Program Conclusion)
Madam Gu,

108
00:06:45,759 --> 00:06:46,439
(Charity Recovery Program Conclusion)
thank you for giving us the chance

109
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,000
(Charity Recovery Program Conclusion)
to recover in such a beautiful place.

110
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:49,560
You even brought us the best doctors.

111
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,720
Thank you, Madam Gu.

112
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,360
Without your help,

113
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,040
our skin would not have healed so fast.

114
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:53,639
Yes.

115
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,480
This world is so superficial.

116
00:06:55,759 --> 00:06:57,399
A lot of girls are insecure
about their looks.

117
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,720
This opens the door
for dishonest businesses.

118
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:02,319
They abuse drugs for quick profits,

119
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:04,839
but we end up paying the price.

120
00:07:05,439 --> 00:07:06,360
I hope every girl

121
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,839
can use good,

122
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:08,920
safe products,

123
00:07:09,199 --> 00:07:10,040
and stay healthy and beautiful.

124
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,879
Our resort is always open to everyone.

125
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,199
Thank you, Madam Gu.

126
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,439
You are Gu Qingmei?

127
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:19,800
Then who am I?

128
00:07:24,079 --> 00:07:24,759
Su Li.

129
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:28,800
How does it feel to live a life
that isn't yours?

130
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:30,680
Two Gu Qingmei?

131
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:31,839
They are identical!

132
00:07:33,279 --> 00:07:34,160
Look closely!

133
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:37,040
I am the real Gu Qingmei.

134
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:45,040
Are you lawyers from Shengda Group?

135
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,279
Yes, Miss Su.

136
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,959
Mr. He sent us

137
00:07:48,199 --> 00:07:50,360
to verify Gu Qingmei's identity.

138
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:53,319
My father-in-law saw through you
long time ago.

139
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:54,959
He sent me back

140
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,800
to expose you.

141
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,800
If you know what's good for you,

142
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,560
you'll leave now.

143
00:08:01,759 --> 00:08:02,560
(Miss,)

144
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:04,120
(the year you were born,)

145
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,639
(you were swept away by a flood.)

146
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:07,480
(Everyone thought you were gone.)

147
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,639
If you hand over Gu Corporation,

148
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,600
I will let you leave with dignity.

149
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:14,160
Otherwise,

150
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:16,160
do you want

151
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,040
a taste of prison life?

152
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:22,360
These were always yours.

153
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,319
I never wanted to take them.

154
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:26,160
That's easy for you to say.

155
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,040
How many people have you deceived

156
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:29,279
using my identity?

157
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:31,480
What did I deceive them about?

158
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,639
She is not a liar.

159
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,679
She is a good person.

160
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:36,360
- Yes.
- Yes. She's a good person.

161
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,279
She helped us.

162
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,480
She's not a liar.

163
00:08:38,759 --> 00:08:39,559
She's not a liar.

164
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,679
If you don't leave now,

165
00:08:40,879 --> 00:08:41,799
I will call the police

166
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,919
and report you for identity fraud
and attempted scam.

167
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,480
There is no good person
in the He family.

168
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,519
Be careful.

169
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,120
You are a fake.

170
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,360
You have no right to tell me what to do.

171
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,480
I'm the sole heir of Gu Corporation.

172
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:01,960
Who are you?

173
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,519
I never expected

174
00:09:12,679 --> 00:09:14,080
you to be a fake all along.

175
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,519
You have been occupying
her place for so long.

176
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:16,919
Finally, it's time for you to leave.

177
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,879
Are you here to laugh at me too?

178
00:09:22,679 --> 00:09:25,039
We are getting engaged next week.

179
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:27,840
An imposter like you
has no right to attend.

180
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:30,919
Mu Shaoze,

181
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,480
aren't you going to say something?

182
00:09:34,639 --> 00:09:35,879
After playing Gu Qingmei for so long,

183
00:09:36,279 --> 00:09:38,000
have you forgotten who you really are?

184
00:09:39,399 --> 00:09:40,559
I only got close to you before

185
00:09:41,279 --> 00:09:42,120
because

186
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:44,519
you were the Chairman of Gu Corporation.

187
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:46,360
That made you

188
00:09:46,639 --> 00:09:47,639
useful to me.

189
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,519
Now that I have no use anymore,

190
00:09:50,559 --> 00:09:51,679
you turn your back on me?

191
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,759
Surely you don't think

192
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:54,919
I care who the real Gu Qingmei is?

193
00:09:55,559 --> 00:09:56,440
As for me,

194
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:59,519
I only care about who means more to me.

195
00:10:00,159 --> 00:10:01,080
Mu Shaoze,

196
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,320
you wretch!

197
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,320
We come from matching families.

198
00:10:04,519 --> 00:10:05,440
We have been engaged since childhood.

199
00:10:05,759 --> 00:10:07,080
If you know what's good for you,

200
00:10:07,559 --> 00:10:10,080
get lost and never come back.

201
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:10,519
You...

202
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,039
Exactly.

203
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:15,039
Go back to where you came from.

204
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:16,919
Let's go.

205
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:19,320
Bye.

206
00:10:28,039 --> 00:10:28,519
Su Li.

207
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,480
I'll find a place for you to stay.

208
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:38,799
Are you planning to keep a mistress?

209
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:41,759
Weren't you so sure of yourself before?

210
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,919
And now look what happened.

211
00:10:43,279 --> 00:10:44,080
Does it sting?

212
00:10:44,559 --> 00:10:45,080
I'm sorry.

213
00:10:46,039 --> 00:10:47,159
I have no choice.

214
00:11:00,799 --> 00:11:01,519
Is that enough?

215
00:11:02,279 --> 00:11:03,000
He Jinxi,

216
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,799
don't forget what you promised me.

217
00:11:13,679 --> 00:11:15,279
(As long as I have you first,)

218
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:16,679
(one day,)

219
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,559
(I will win your heart.)

220
00:11:21,159 --> 00:11:21,840
Su Li,

221
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:22,879
you...

222
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,879
Fine, I can be with you,

223
00:11:30,639 --> 00:11:32,240
but you have to divorce Gu Qingmei,

224
00:11:32,759 --> 00:11:34,240
clean and simple.

225
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:35,360
I...

226
00:11:37,679 --> 00:11:38,039
I...

227
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,120
I can't do that right now.

228
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:40,799
You can't?

229
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:42,840
Or you don't want to?

230
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:46,159
He Jinchen.

231
00:11:46,759 --> 00:11:47,879
You know perfectly well

232
00:11:48,159 --> 00:11:50,559
that they only see Gu Qingmei as a pawn.

233
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,360
You act all sweet with me,

234
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:54,519
while enjoying all the benefits
she brings.

235
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,879
You're such a selfish opportunist.

236
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:59,000
You don't deserve to talk about love.

237
00:11:59,399 --> 00:12:00,519
Your little schemes

238
00:12:00,679 --> 00:12:02,159
are not fooling anyone.

239
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:05,039
Su Li,

240
00:12:05,559 --> 00:12:07,279
although profit is what I value most,

241
00:12:07,679 --> 00:12:08,799
no matter who you are,

242
00:12:09,559 --> 00:12:10,639
my feelings for you are real.

243
00:12:20,759 --> 00:12:21,960
You like me even when I'm this wild?

244
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,679
Yes.

245
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:30,240
I like a woman who challenges me.

246
00:12:31,039 --> 00:12:32,440
How pathetic.

247
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,279
Listen,

248
00:12:35,519 --> 00:12:36,679
stop bothering me.

249
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:38,000
If you keep doing that,

250
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:40,240
I will hit you every time I see you.

251
00:13:02,559 --> 00:13:03,080
Hey, sis.

252
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,120
Who's your sis?

253
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,200
The Gu family's old nanny told me

254
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,559
we are twins.

255
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:11,960
So what?

256
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,399
Are you still eyeing Gu Corporation

257
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:17,080
and trying to take my place?

258
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:19,879
I'm not interested in any of that.

259
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:22,240
I only want to find evidence
of the He family's crimes.

260
00:13:24,639 --> 00:13:25,639
Why are you telling me this?

261
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:27,039
They are too dangerous.

262
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:28,919
I'm worried you can't handle them alone.

263
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:29,879
Let's work together.

264
00:13:32,279 --> 00:13:34,080
I have everything in Gu Corporation now.

265
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,320
Why would I work with you?

266
00:13:35,639 --> 00:13:36,600
They only brought you back

267
00:13:36,799 --> 00:13:39,080
to use you as a puppet
to drain Gu Corporation.

268
00:13:39,399 --> 00:13:40,840
Do you want to be manipulated

269
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:41,720
by them forever?

270
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,240
Don't you want to fight back?

271
00:14:09,340 --> 00:14:14,100
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

272
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:18,940
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

273
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:23,500
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

274
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:28,420
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

275
00:14:28,420 --> 00:14:32,220
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

276
00:14:32,220 --> 00:14:37,020
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

277
00:14:37,020 --> 00:14:39,860
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

278
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:42,540
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

279
00:14:42,900 --> 00:14:48,460
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

280
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:55,660
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

281
00:14:55,940 --> 00:15:00,620
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

282
00:15:00,780 --> 00:15:07,580
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

283
00:15:07,900 --> 00:15:14,700
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

284
